        "reaction_type_english": "Cracking reaction",
        "description": "使用Ni/Meso-Y催化剂在390°C和3MPa氢气压力下将棕榈油转化为喷气燃料范围的烃类。棕榈油部分直接裂解为C8-C14烷烃，部分通过脱羰基化转化为C15-C18烷烃，后者进一步裂解或脱氢芳构化。",
        "text_snippet": "Zeolite Ni/Meso-Y exhibited the highest jet range alkane yield (30.7%)... palm oil directly cracked into C8–C14 alkanes over Ni/Meso-Y.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Cracking reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "裂解反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Cracking reaction",
        "description": "使用Ni/Meso-Hbeta催化剂在390°C和3MPa氢气压力下将棕榈油转化为喷气燃料。棕榈油通过脱羰基化转化为C15-C17烷烃，这些烷烃进一步裂解为C8-C14烷烃或通过芳构化转化为芳香烃。",
        "text_snippet": "Zeolite Meso-Hbeta presented a moderate jet range alkane yield of 26.9%, and a jet range aromatic hydrocarbon yield of 19%... palm oil deoxygenated to C15–C17 alkane through decarbonylation.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Cracking reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 3,
        "reaction_type": "裂解反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Cracking reaction",
        "description": "使用Ni/Meso-HZSM-5催化剂在390°C和3MPa氢气压力下将棕榈油转化为烃类。棕榈油主要通过脱羰基化直接转化为芳香烃，部分转化为C15-C17烷烃，后者进一步裂解或芳构化。",
        "text_snippet": "Zeolite Meso-HZSM-5 presented the lowest jet range alkane yield of 3.2%, and the highest jet range aromatic hydrocarbon yield of 28.3%... part of palm oil was directly converted into aromatic hydrocarbons through decarbonylation.",
